{"type": "article", "id": 40004, "title": "这台会下雨的机器，想让你更直观地感受天气｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-04-20T23:09:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 22454, "name": "MUT Design"}, {"id": 39676, "name": "Sancal"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 216, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170420210105kLm2g4ue8fSrCo3M.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Hello from the weather by Ellie Zeng</h3><p>尽管能知晓天气情况的途径变多了，我们得到的也仅仅是枯燥的数据而已，要确定自己是不是穿对了衣服，我们往往还得走到户外感受下温度才行。针对体感上的这一缺失，广州大学的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/978240143a094\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ellie Zeng</a> 构思了一款让天气预报变得更有趣的概念机器，并将它取名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/46352413/Hello-from-the-weather\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hello from the weather</a>。只要将手放到屏幕下方，内部的装置会根据当前的温度和天气让你直接地感受到户外的状况。更有趣的是，机器的顶端还会根据当天的天气变化配合屏幕上的时间轴相应地调整对应的符号。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210131HhPacfi0Ge9jzbMm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210132fjFGbSo0Ky8Rguwd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704202101329U6qmry5IfF2DRSQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210132ex7WJky8mpZUblPD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210132D3I8GNPf5uwcy0JM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210132FOLiNQK5RHD7ArYG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Jsouv by Kostya Kolesov</h3><p>来自俄罗斯的 <a href=\"http://www.koskolesov.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kostya Kolesov</a> 是一名喜欢周游世界的设计师，每次旅行他都会在当地找寻一些具有代表性的装饰品带回家珍藏。最近，他挑选了自己参观过的 15 个来自世界各地的标志性建筑物，将它们制作成一套名为 Jsouv 的桌面摆件。金属切割而成的建筑物通过磁贴和刻有 2D 版建筑形象的木制底座吸附在一起，小巧但不失精致感。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/jsouv-tiny-sculptures-of-iconic-architecture-travel#/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 29 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210201H5ewSso1XK0T3WgB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564516\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210201NApGhc1fVEMJ7I83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.491935\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210202LnZkIJHOMSGiYzRw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.174194\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210201zhK3a4nfgA7H0PJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.100000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cross Guitar</h3><p>为了帮助人们突破空间限制，随时随地都能弹奏吉他，来自台湾的设计团队开发了一款名为好哲琴的折叠式吉他。相比其他主打便携性以至于省略到仅有琴格的产品，好哲琴将占地方的桶身结构转换为支架形态，还原出弹奏吉他的状态，在一定程度上减轻了违和感。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.flyingv.cc/projects/15475\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从新台币 3680 元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210414xJF6Wk3nNEmIupQS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.372970\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210415vsJjApGwZ15qcnLi.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210414klRAW0LJabQpCmej.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210414xeyv5ldQnmph78Gw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Beetle by MUT Design</h3><p>谁说消音板不能变成一件有趣的装饰品？西班牙设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.mutdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MUT Design</a> 最近就以一次自然博物馆之行中所观察到的昆虫标本为灵感，为家居品牌 <a href=\"http://www.sancal.com/home.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sancal</a> 打造了这套名为 Beetle 的模块化消音板。用户可以从五种形状的消音板中任选三片固定在橡木制的底座上，底座本身也可以涂上不同的颜色，这种灵活的组合方式就好像大自然中的甲虫那样丰富多元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210222urL5SPOTbiQqGpmn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.808068\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210222CR3eBGEIYXspODQa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.808068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210223xOrQawBR0KbS7mgn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.855746\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210223cA7XYnH0fyZpT2kP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.808068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210222EzWuXgkqpxOj0rci.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.808068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>SAIKAI by Maja Ahlund et al.</h3><p>在瑞典，就着零食和朋友一起喝上一杯咖啡的休息时间被称为 Fika。最近，瑞典中部大学包装设计系的四位学生在与日本同学交流 Fika 体验后，为针对当地市场的日本茶点构思了一个名为 SAIKAI（意为再会）的概念品牌。六边形的纸盒上印有灵感源自高山、河流、农田等自然风光的抽象图案，红绿两色分别代表了仙贝和绿茶叶两种产品。纸盒为了保护仙贝特意采用了折叠式的结构和独立的插槽，展开后就转变为三组可以轻松取食的托盘，看起来就像是山脉一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210248pM4jf621uRc5gisr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704202102484nSMeHUk2Aru0mGF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210248E52BtcMsuhybrApU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210248OFtP86E3T21D5Rl9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210248E2hFnLSfleZGYbaM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Shadow Spaces by Owen Gildersleeve &amp; Stephen Lenthall</h3><p>看到这组出自英国静物摄影师 <a href=\"http://www.lenthall.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stephen Lenthall</a> 的照片时，你或许会以为它们是某个美术馆的内部。实际上，这套名为 <a href=\"http://owengildersleeve.com/showcase/shadow-spaces\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shadow Spaces</a> 的作品拍摄的是艺术家 <a href=\"http://owengildersleeve.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Owen Gildersleeve</a> 搭建的小型纸模，他们希望通过这种方式帮助人们从另一种角度理解空间、形状与光影之间的联系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210308o0rSLfgBH9cNtGxJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333721\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210308OQ57fWZjtqzCJed8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333721\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210308eChEcWXrJVi2zOHd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210308c7fYKQbWIjmJ8MVe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210309lIMOt1eWcZf8UhdH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332558\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170420210309qr0bSTHsnJuol7eV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}